<section class="membership-page">
    <section class="member-hero">
        <div class="member-hero-copy">
            <span class="eyebrow">FRESH MEAT MEMBERSHIP</span>
            <h1>단골로 등록하시면 더욱 특별한 가격이 찾아 갑니다.</h1>
            <p>자주 사는 부위와 식탁 스타일을 남겨두면 매장에서 더 빠르게 추천하고, 혜택도 바로 챙겨드립니다.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="membership-shell">
        <%- include('../../partials/brand-spirit-card', { className: 'member-spirit-card brand-spirit-card' }) %>

        <main class="member-main">
            <form action="/membership/register" method="POST" class="member-form">
                <div class="member-form-columns">
                    <div class="member-form-column">
                        <div class="form-block">
                            <div class="form-section">
                                <span class="step">01</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h2>기본 정보</h2>
                                    <p>매장에서 단골 정보를 찾을 때 사용하는 정보입니다.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-grid">
                                <label class="field">
                                    <span>이름</span>
                                    <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="홍길동" autocomplete="name">
                                </label>
                                <label class="field">
                                    <span>연락처</span>
                                    <input type="tel" name="phone" required placeholder="01012345678" autocomplete="tel" inputmode="tel">
                                </label>
                            </div>

                            <label class="field">
                                <span>텔레그램 ID</span>
                                <input type="text" name="telegram_id" placeholder="@freshmeat">
                                <small>입력하면 행사 안내와 5,000P 혜택을 받을 수 있습니다.</small>
                            </label>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-block">
                            <div class="form-section">
                                <span class="step">02</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h2>구매 취향</h2>
                                    <p>추천 정확도를 높이기 위한 선택 정보입니다.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-grid">
                                <label class="field">
                                    <span>자주 찾는 고기</span>
                                    <select name="preferred_meat">
                                        <option value="beef">소고기</option>
                                        <option value="pork">돼지고기</option>
                                        <option value="chicken">닭고기</option>
                                        <option value="mixed">상황별로 다름</option>
                                    </select>
                                </label>
                                <label class="field">
                                    <span>주 이용 시간</span>
                                    <select name="visit_time">
                                        <option value="morning">오전</option>
                                        <option value="lunch">점심</option>
                                        <option value="evening">저녁</option>
                                        <option value="weekend">주말</option>
                                    </select>
                                </label>
                            </div>

                            <div class="chip-group" aria-label="구매 스타일">
                                <label><input type="radio" name="shopping_style" value="family" checked><span>가족 식사</span></label>
                                <label><input type="radio" name="shopping_style" value="solo"><span>1인 소포장</span></label>
                                <label><input type="radio" name="shopping_style" value="camping"><span>캠핑/바비큐</span></label>
                                <label><input type="radio" name="shopping_style" value="fitness"><span>식단 관리</span></label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="member-form-column">
                        <div class="form-block">
                            <div class="form-section">
                                <span class="step">03</span>
                                <div>
                                    <h2>혜택 방식 선택</h2>
                                    <p>매장 운영에 맞춰 바로 상담할 수 있게 구분합니다.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="choice-grid">
                                <label class="choice-card">
                                    <input type="radio" name="membership_type" value="basic" checked>
                                    <span>
                                        <i class="fas fa-id-card"></i>
                                        <strong>기본 단골</strong>
                                        <small>포인트 적립과 행사 안내</small>
                                    </span>
                                </label>
                                <label class="choice-card">
                                    <input type="radio" name="membership_type" value="prepaid">
                                    <span>
                                        <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
                                        <strong>선불 충전</strong>
                                        <small>충전 고객 전용 추가 혜택</small>
                                    </span>
                                </label>
                                <label class="choice-card">
                                    <input type="radio" name="membership_type" value="subscription">
                                    <span>
                                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
                                        <strong>정기 구독</strong>
                                        <small>월 단위 고기 패키지 상담</small>
                                    </span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-block">
                            <label class="agree-row">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="marketing_agree" value="1">
                                <span>행사, 입고, 쿠폰 안내를 받겠습니다.</span>
                            </label>

                            <button type="submit" class="submit-button">
                                단골 등록 완료하기 <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </main>

        <aside class="benefit-panel">
            <div class="member-benefit-card">
                <img src="/images/fresh-meat-logo.png" alt="프레시미트">
                <strong>등록 즉시 1,000P</strong>
                <span>텔레그램 ID 입력 시 5,000P 지급</span>
            </div>
            <span class="panel-label">단골 혜택</span>
            <h2>매번 묻지 않아도 알아서 맞춰드리는 정육 서비스</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 선호 부위와 용도 기반 추천</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 행사 상품 우선 안내</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 포인트 적립 및 단골 등급 관리</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 명절, 캠핑, 홈파티 세트 빠른 예약</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="benefit-stats">
                <div>
                    <strong>3초</strong>
                    <span>연락처 조회</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <strong>5,000P</strong>
                    <span>연동 혜택</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.membership-page {
    background: #f8f3ea;
    padding: 0 0 70px;
}
.member-hero {
    margin: 0 0 34px;
    padding: 56px 20px 34px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
    background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(23, 75, 50, 0.78), rgba(143, 23, 29, 0.65)),
        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1603048297172-c92544798d5a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=85') center/cover;
}
.member-hero-copy {
    width: min(1180px, 100%);
}
.member-hero h1 {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 10px auto 12px;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.4vw, 3.25rem);
    line-height: 1.04;
    white-space: nowrap;
}
.member-hero p {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1.04rem;
}
.member-benefit-card {
    background: #fffdf8;
    border: 1px solid #eadfce;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
}
.member-benefit-card img {
    width: 82px;
    height: 64px;
    object-fit: contain;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.member-benefit-card strong,
.member-benefit-card span {
    display: block;
}
.member-benefit-card strong {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.28rem;
}
.member-benefit-card span {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 6px;
}
.membership-shell {
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 clamp(18px, 3vw, 48px);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px minmax(0, 1fr) 220px;
    gap: clamp(16px, 2vw, 28px);
    align-items: start;
}
.member-main {
    min-width: 0;
    max-width: none;
}
.benefit-panel,
.member-form {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 42px rgba(66, 42, 18, 0.07);
}
.benefit-panel {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(50vh - 250px);
    padding: 18px;
    justify-self: end;
    width: 220px;
}
.member-spirit-card {
    position: sticky;
    top: 104px;
}
.panel-label {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
}
.benefit-panel h2 {
    margin: 10px 0 18px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.25;
}
.benefit-panel ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
}
.benefit-panel li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.45;
}
.benefit-panel i {
    color: var(--green);
    margin-top: 3px;
}
.benefit-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
}
.benefit-stats div {
    background: var(--paper);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 14px;
}
.benefit-stats strong,
.benefit-stats span {
    display: block;
}
.benefit-stats strong {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
}
.benefit-stats span {
    margin-top: 3px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
}
.member-form {
    padding: 26px;
}
.member-form-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 22px;
    align-items: start;
}
.member-form-column {
    display: grid;
    gap: 22px;
}
.form-block {
    min-width: 0;
}
.form-section {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin: 4px 0 18px;
}
.step {
    width: 38px;
    height: 38px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
}
.form-section h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.28rem;
}
.form-section p {
    margin: 4px 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.45;
}
.form-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
}
.field {
    display: grid;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.field span {
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--green);
}
.field input,
.field select,
.field textarea {
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #fffdf8;
    padding: 14px;
    font: inherit;
    color: var(--ink);
    outline: none;
}
.field input:focus,
.field select:focus,
.field textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(143, 23, 29, 0.1);
}
.field small {
    color: var(--muted);
}
.choice-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 26px;
}
.choice-card {
    cursor: pointer;
}
.choice-card input,
.chip-group input {
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0;
}
.choice-card > span {
    min-height: 104px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 18px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: #fffdf8;
}
.choice-card i {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
}
.choice-card strong {
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 1.06rem;
}
.choice-card small {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.35;
}
.choice-card input:checked + span {
    background: #fff2f1;
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px var(--primary);
}
.chip-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
}
.chip-group label span {
    display: inline-flex;
    min-height: 40px;
    align-items: center;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 9px 14px;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 800;
    cursor: pointer;
}
.chip-group input:checked + span {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #fff;
    border-color: var(--green);
}
.agree-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 12px 0 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
}
.agree-row input {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    accent-color: var(--primary);
}
.submit-button {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 56px;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    font: inherit;
    font-weight: 800;
    cursor: pointer;
}
@media (max-width: 860px) {
    .membership-shell,
    .member-form-columns,
    .form-grid,
    .choice-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .member-hero {
        margin-bottom: 22px;
        padding: 44px 16px 28px;
        text-align: left;
    }
    .membership-shell {
        padding: 0 16px;
    }
    .benefit-panel {
        position: static;
        padding: 20px;
        width: 100%;
    }
    .member-spirit-card {
        position: static;
    }
    .member-form {
        padding: 20px;
    }
    .member-hero h1 {
        font-size: 2.35rem;
        white-space: normal;
    }
}
</style>
